---
import { colorPalettes } from "@config";
---

<section id="color" class="border-t-[1.5px] border-ink bg-paper-warm py-20 md:py-24">
  <div class="container-shell">
    <div class="mb-12 flex flex-wrap items-end justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <p class="font-display text-lg font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-orange">02 / Color</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 font-display text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem)] font-semibold leading-none tracking-normal">Naranja, negro,<br />y un toque de sol.</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="max-w-md leading-7 text-gray-700">
        Nuestra paleta es simple a propósito: <strong>negro + naranja + blanco</strong> hacen el 90% del trabajo. Los acentos entran para posts de redes e ilustraciones específicas.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h3 class="mb-4 font-display text-xl font-semibold tracking-normal">Base</h3>
    <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      {
        colorPalettes.base.map((swatch) => (
          <article class:list={["brand-outline flex min-h-44 flex-col justify-between rounded-brand-lg p-6", swatch.className]}>
            <h4 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-normal">{swatch.name}</h4>
            <div class="flex justify-between text-xs font-bold uppercase opacity-80">
              <span>{swatch.hex}</span>
              <span>{swatch.token}</span>
            </div>
          </article>
        ))
      }
    </div>

    <h3 class="mb-4 mt-10 font-display text-xl font-semibold tracking-normal">Acentos (uso moderado)</h3>
    <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      {
        colorPalettes.accents.map((swatch) => (
          <article class:list={["brand-outline flex min-h-44 flex-col justify-between rounded-brand-lg p-6", swatch.className]}>
            <h4 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-normal">{swatch.name}</h4>
            <div class="flex justify-between text-xs font-bold uppercase opacity-80">
              <span>{swatch.hex}</span>
              <span>{swatch.token}</span>
            </div>
          </article>
        ))
      }
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 rounded-brand-lg bg-ink p-6 text-paper">
      <strong class="font-display text-lg font-semibold">Regla 60-30-10</strong>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300">60% blanco o crema · 30% tinta negra · 10% naranja. Los acentos entran ocasionalmente para posts, ilustraciones o celebraciones.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
